---
---
<section class="section testimonials" id="reviews">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-header center animate-fadeUp">
      <div class="section-tag">Real Stories</div>
      <h2 class="heading-lg">3,847 Families <span class="text-gradient-gold">Trust PackersHub</span></h2>
      <p style="color:var(--gray-600); max-width:500px; margin:16px auto 0;">
        Don't take our word for it. Here's what our customers say after their experience with us.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="testimonials-grid">
      <div class="testimonial-card animate-fadeUp">
        <div class="testimonial-badge">Verified ✓</div>
        <div class="testimonial-stars">★★★★★</div>
        <p class="testimonial-text">Moved from Nellore to Hyderabad and I couldn't believe how smooth it was. Not a single item broken. The team was punctual, professional, and even helped me set up my new home. PackersHub has set a new standard for moving!</p>
        <div class="testimonial-author">
          <div class="testimonial-avatar">SR</div>
          <div>
            <div class="testimonial-name">Srinivas Reddy</div>
            <div class="testimonial-loc">📍 Nellore → Hyderabad</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="testimonial-card animate-fadeUp" style="animation-delay: 0.1s;">
        <div class="testimonial-badge">Verified ✓</div>
        <div class="testimonial-stars">★★★★★</div>
        <p class="testimonial-text">I was very nervous about my antique furniture. The PackersHub team wrapped each piece individually with extra care. Everything arrived in Bangalore in perfect condition. The GPS tracking was a wonderful feature!</p>
        <div class="testimonial-author">
          <div class="testimonial-avatar">LK</div>
          <div>
            <div class="testimonial-name">Lakshmi Krishnan</div>
            <div class="testimonial-loc">📍 Chennai → Bengaluru</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="testimonial-card animate-fadeUp" style="animation-delay: 0.2s;">
        <div class="testimonial-badge">Verified ✓</div>
        <div class="testimonial-stars">★★★★★</div>
        <p class="testimonial-text">PackersHub relocated our entire office in Hyderabad over a weekend. Monday morning, we walked into a fully set up workplace. Zero downtime, zero damage. Absolutely phenomenal service from a phenomenal team!</p>
        <div class="testimonial-author">
          <div class="testimonial-avatar">AM</div>
          <div>
            <div class="testimonial-name">Arun Mehta</div>
            <div class="testimonial-loc">📍 Office Move, Hyderabad</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="testimonial-card animate-fadeUp" style="animation-delay: 0.3s;">
        <div class="testimonial-badge">Verified ✓</div>
        <div class="testimonial-stars">★★★★★</div>
        <p class="testimonial-text">Their pricing is transparent and they don't add hidden charges at the last moment like other companies. I used them twice — once in Vijayawada, once Kochi — and both experiences were exceptional!</p>
        <div class="testimonial-author">
          <div class="testimonial-avatar">PV</div>
          <div>
            <div class="testimonial-name">Priya Venkatesh</div>
            <div class="testimonial-loc">📍 Vijayawada → Kochi</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="testimonial-card animate-fadeUp" style="animation-delay: 0.4s;">
        <div class="testimonial-badge">Verified ✓</div>
        <div class="testimonial-stars">★★★★★</div>
        <p class="testimonial-text">I was shifting with two kids and a dog. PackersHub handled everything with patience and care. They even helped my kids label their boxes! This company understands that moving is emotional, not just physical.</p>
        <div class="testimonial-author">
          <div class="testimonial-avatar">NG</div>
          <div>
            <div class="testimonial-name">Nirmala Gowda</div>
            <div class="testimonial-loc">📍 Mysuru → Coimbatore</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="testimonial-card animate-fadeUp" style="animation-delay: 0.5s;">
        <div class="testimonial-badge">Verified ✓</div>
        <div class="testimonial-stars">★★★★★</div>
        <p class="testimonial-text">Car transport from Visakhapatnam to Thiruvananthapuram — my car arrived without a single scratch and ahead of schedule. The enclosed carrier and full insurance gave me total peace of mind. Highly recommended!</p>
        <div class="testimonial-author">
          <div class="testimonial-avatar">RN</div>
          <div>
            <div class="testimonial-name">Rajesh Nair</div>
            <div class="testimonial-loc">📍 Vizag → Thiruvananthapuram</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div style="text-align:center; margin-top:48px;" class="animate-fadeUp">
      <div style="display:inline-flex; align-items:center; gap:20px; flex-wrap:wrap; justify-content:center;">
        <span class="badge badge-gold">⭐ 4.9/5 Google Rating</span>
        <span class="badge badge-blue">🔵 3,847 Reviews</span>
        <span class="badge badge-olive">✅ 98% Recommend Rate</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .testimonials { background: var(--gray-50); padding: 100px 0; }
  .testimonials-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 24px;
    margin-top: 60px;
  }
  .testimonial-card {
    background: var(--white);
    padding: 40px;
    border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
    border: 1px solid var(--gray-100);
    position: relative;
    transition: var(--transition);
  }
  .testimonial-card:hover { transform: translateY(-8px); border-color: var(--blue-200); box-shadow: var(--shadow-card); }
  .testimonial-badge {
    position: absolute;
    top: 24px;
    right: 32px;
    background: rgba(37,211,102,0.1);
    color: #25D366;
    padding: 4px 12px;
    border-radius: 100px;
    font-size: 11px;
    font-weight: 700;
  }
  .testimonial-stars { color: var(--gold); font-size: 14px; margin-bottom: 20px; letter-spacing: 2px; }
  .testimonial-text { font-size: 15px; color: var(--gray-700); line-height: 1.8; font-style: italic; margin-bottom: 32px; }
  .testimonial-author { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 16px; }
  .testimonial-avatar {
    width: 48px; height: 48px;
    background: var(--gradient-hero);
    color: var(--white);
    border-radius: 50%;
    display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-weight: 700;
    font-size: 14px;
  }
  .testimonial-name { font-family: var(--font-ui); font-weight: 700; color: var(--gray-800); font-size: 15px; }
  .testimonial-loc { font-size: 12px; color: var(--gray-500); margin-top: 2px; }

  @media (max-width: 1024px) {
    .testimonials-grid { grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); }
  }
  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .testimonials-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
  }
</style>
